reviewText:
So these are great shoes.  You get what you pay for.  So understand that I use these shoes for weightlifting or running.  They aren't exactly for basketball or soccer or sports. Cutting at angles may be difficult. But these shoes are great for their purpose.  One thing to keep in mind is that I expected them to fit small, so I ordered a size larger.  That being in mind, I did say they fit as expected, but that's because I expected them to fit small.  Great shoes. Very comfortable, look great, and stylish.  I like that I can be active in them.
Comfortable fabric and rubber sole.
Lightweight, durable textile fabric with specific flexibility;
Slip resistance, durable rubber sole against abrasion;
Classic low-top sneaker featuring four-eyelet drawstring closure for easy on and off; Two ways to wear on: Slip on and Lace up ;
Suit for sports, party, indoor, outdoor and any occasion, casual and trend; Design for perfect fit and comfort, stability and speed;

They are like knock of yeezys that look and feel great.  I was happy to get them at a discounted price.  They are a good shoe and I recommend them.
